                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9064" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0116</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1657 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">路虽弥，行则至：陆盾的危与机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Road is Mile-High: Crises and Opportunities for Lu Dun</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙利娟，邢小军，陈汉辉，武佩剑，王霄，王汉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陆盾机械制造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造业；企业资源与能力；成长企业；专精特新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mechanical Assembly; Resources and Capacities; Growing Company；SRDI</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制造业是强国之基。疫情冲击下，实体经济尤其是传统制造业发展放缓、出口受阻，如何破局关系到高质量发展与国计民生。本案例为描述性案例，讲述了陆盾机械制造有限公司成立十七年以来，在两代三人的带领下生产与管理转型之路，对陆盾存续期间遭遇的若干困局与纾解之策进行了详尽梳理，并探讨了不确定动态条件下传统制造业企业成长问题。本案例旨在引起对传统制造型中小企业出口与发展的关注，深化案例使用者对企业资源与能力的理解，激发对于不确定动态条件下企业成长问题的思考，并为同类型企业提供有益参考。同时，工匠精神与敬业诚信构成了陆盾两代三人的精神内核，支撑企业渡过众多难关。案例将上述思政元素融入案例编写，通过案例研习强化课程思政效果。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Manufacturing is the foundation of a strong country. Under the impact of the epidemic, the real economy, especially the traditional manufacturing industry slowed down and exports are blocked. How to break the dilemma is related to the high-quality development. This case is a descriptive case which tells the production and management of the transformation of Lu Dun Machinery Manufacturing Co., Ltd. under the leadership of two generations. The case introduces the survival of Lu Dun encountered during the dilemma and the relief measures for a detailed compendium, and discusses the traditional manufacturing enterprise growth issues under the uncertainty of the dynamic conditions. The case aims to draw attention to the export and development of traditional manufacturing SMEs, deepen the case users’ understanding of enterprise resources and capabilities, stimulate thinking about the growth of enterprises under uncertain dynamic conditions, and provide useful reference for similar enterprises. Meanwhile, craftsmanship， dedication and integrity constitute the spiritual core of two generations of Lu Dun, supporting the enterprise through many difficulties. The case is written with the integration of such ideological and political elements, so as to strengthen the ideological and political effect of the course through the case study.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业管理》、《国际商务》、《全球商务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业资源与能力;VRIO框架（价值-稀缺-可模仿-组织性）;不确定环境中企业资源与能力成长</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
